      <p><a href="ch76s29.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)238">Uvuudaums</a> can speak telepathically to any creature within 500 feet that has a language.<a href="img/EpicMonsters(G-W).Uvuudaum.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/EpicMonsters(G-W).Uvuudaum.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A <a href="ch76s29.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)238">uvuudaum's</a> natural weapons are treated as epic and evil for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
